The reason that your next income leap is evading you is that your TRAUMA RESPONSE is activated because on some level you feel on safe to take the leap.

Maybe not useless, but definitely restful ;)

What about you?

When you’re used to speaking to needy clients, there is a level of unconscious mastery that takes over

You’re so used to the projections of:

“I can’t move forward without you!”

“I need all of your time in order for me to achieve x!”

“I need you to motivate me!”

“I’ll be able to finally achieve x, once I fix y!”

[Insert other illusion here]

Speaking to and serving a premium client leaves you feeling like a fish out of water, you wonder why they aren't 'biting'

It’s a very different language, and it requires your need to be needed to dissolve…..quickly! Serving from and into neediness is costing you millions.

She leads herself, is clear on who she is, what she wants, and how to resource herself.

She doesn’t need you, she desires to get access to your wisdom, so that she can move quickly.

She doesn’t need to consume endless freebies to decide if you are an aligned mentor for her.

She will refuse to read a sales letter that is longer than 2 paragraphs.

She wants to be seen & held in her highest potential, to be treated as highly capable & wise.

There is a way to speak to a high minded woman such that your $50K, $100k, $250K offers sell themselves without ads, mass content, sales calls, a robust funnels and more.

I can help you speak to this calibre of woman, successfully fill your ultra premium offers with ease & elegance, so that you can enjoy 6 figures months (even weeks) working only with the dreamiest clients who are so fun to co-create with.

They will show up with honor, ready to move, and will pay you very well w/o any drama or pity story.

If you are truly ready to serve this level of client, and to move quickly to burst through your income ceiling, and to finally enjoy 6 figure months/weeks, I'm ready to pour my 8 figure strategies into you.

There are 2 accelerated ways we can work together. Message me for more info.

You can’t chant your way to consistent 6 figure months, but you can choose it, and if it’s not showing up yet, it’s because of 2 reasons:

i) you’ve contemplated the possibility but you haven’t really chosen it; decision is a potent activator and necessary first step in manifesting anything.

ii) the same actions that brought you to mid 5 figure months, simply won’t propel you into 6 figure months. This is the easy part since all it requires is an aligned business framework to successfully implement and 6 figure months are inevitable!

Many only choose to show up when they ‘need’ the money, and then wonder why they have so many income up’s and down’s (it’s quite stressful to run a business that is not fuelled by predictable, repeatable income)

Many declare they want massive income leaps but then don’t live through the lens of “how does a 7 figure CEO start her day, lead her team, focus her time, network with, etc?” In other words they want the results but aren’t willing to line up their actions to support the shift.

The high level woman knows that she must decide, she must align that decision in all of her actions, and she must call in mentorship to help her get to her next level quickly because she values her time and knows that investing in guidance to create speed is invaluable.

The high level woman is so committed to her sacred mission that investing in it's expansion is non-negotiable.

She doesn't need to be convinced to show up for her mission, her community, her growth because her calling is bigger than her desire to stay comfortable.

She bores easily when she is not being stretched into her fullest potential, she bores easily of her money goals because they aren't as big as they could be if she allowed them to be, so......

If you are getting bored with your income ceiling, you’re ready to leap quickly, and you are fully betting on yourself, I have something for you.

Message me to learn the 2 different ways that I can help you leap into your next income level quickly that doesn't require more effort.

The Universe has its own divine timing, and what's meant for you will never miss you. 🕰️✨

Motivational posts ‘seem’ like they’re coming from a good place, right?!

But, when you dig underneath they are feeding the inverted triangle created and perpetuated by the matrix: saving, suffering, sacrificing

When you motivate in your content, you are repelling premium clients since they are already motivated and feel ‘splained’ when you speak to them that way. This is costing you millions.

The truth is, they don’t need saving because they’re not suffering; that is was motivational posts are perpetuating.

The only people that resonate with motivational posts are struggle bunnies because they are still choosing to move through the world as those who suffer and need saving from their circumstances.

In either case, motivational posts either patronize or enable, therefore are not of service.

And the bigger truth is, you make motivational posts because on some level, you are suffering and you need saving. 

It is your need to make these posts in order to a) cheerlead yourself, b) ‘trauma bond’ with other struggle bunnies.

Neediness is fuelling the inverted triangle and is also codependent. This is not the path of the lightleader who is broadcasting everywhere how awake she is!

And that is why premium clients can’t hire you to the degree that you’d like because it is not lost on them who you are really motivating and that you have some unmet/misdirected needs that you still need to work out.
